<section class="ui container pb-16 pt-16 is-light">
  <p class="flow-text">This Radar Renewal Course Series provides an overview of the new modern Dual Polarized S-band radar systems that are gradually coming online at various sites across Canada.  The topics offered explore the S-Band radars, Dual Polarization, new radar products, and key differences within a mixed radar network.  This course series will grow as new products are released and our familiarity with the new radar data matures.</p>

  <p class="flow-text">This fundamentals course series is structured into a series of individual courses.  This offers the flexibility in learning by providing a recommended path while still allowing the freedom that caters to individuals learning needs or interests.  </p>
</section>
